HEADWORD: Orfgild
<hw>Orf"gild`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[AS. <ets>orf</ets>,
<ets>yrfe</ets>, cattle, property + <ets>gild</ets>, <ets>gield</ets>,
money, fine.]</ety> <fld>(O. Eng. Law)</fld> <def>Restitution for
cattle; a penalty for taking away cattle.</def>
<rj><au>Cowell.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
